    "interfaceContracts": [
      "Read → validate → import → persist → clear is transactional.",
      "Ownerless items remain quarantined unless D-DATA-01 authorizes attribution.",
      "Extensions do not open the main app SwiftData store.",
      "Every outbound private shared snapshot carries an opaque owner; WP-ENGAGE-01 publishes it and WP-NOTIFY-01 reads it after this schema integrates.",
      "WP-NATIVE-01 supplies integrated real-localized Share/Action presentation, catalogs, and an explicit pending/committed/failure presentation boundary; this package does not edit those views or catalogs.",
      "The extension capture API is result-bearing and fail-closed: it returns committed only after the complete versioned envelope crosses the declared durability boundary and a fresh reader reopens and decodes the exact mutation.",
      "Share/Action production controllers map committed to the inherited success state and exactly one success announcement before dismissal or app opening; every non-committed result preserves recoverable input and maps to inherited pending/error/retry presentation without false success."
    ]
  },
